Additional Terms for QCF Fonts and QUL Resources

The code in this repository is licensed under the MIT License above. This grant
does not apply to Quranic fonts (QCF) and any tafsir/translation files or other
resources obtained from Quranic Universal Library (QUL) or King Fahd Glorious
Quran Printing Complex (KFGQPC). Those assets are governed by their respective
terms. If you bundle or distribute these assets with your app, you must comply
with the following conditions (summarized from QUL guidance):

1. No distracting ads: Apps or projects must not include advertisements (even
	halal/Islamic ads) that could distract users while reading the Quran.
2. Follow upstream terms: Always comply with KFGQPC and QUL terms when
	distributing applications that include or bundle these assets.

References:
- KFGQPC Developer Portal: https://qurancomplex.gov.sa/quran-dev/
- Quranic Universal Library (QUL): https://qul.tarteel.ai/
